\id 1PE
\h Bira Bhethiroos
\toc1 Kiristoos Yisa Tarjamonnante Kinin Yittsaa Bhethiroosin Thaapoono Birono Warqanno
\toc2 Bira Bhethiroos
\mt2 Kiristoos Yisa Tarjamonnante Kinin Yittsaa
\mt1 Bhethiroosin
\mt2 Thaapoono Birono Warqanno
\is1 Ardinta
\ip Kaa warqatasa thaapadhidino oytadhan goynka wanthimayse dahaana, Barjodar woylamin qajaanana konin dehenka, Bhethiroos gaalesa thoothi kida dhettse. Oytaydhabee gaalebe konin thoothenka Barjodar woylamin qajaa eedi har ki haye? Har ki bhocche? Bhethiroos kaa oysimeana malsin kinin maasenka yer qaabe haydheasa thoothi kida giye. Barjo kodettsin gaalen wodar ko yeske kinin hayenka payyamonbee goninbeysa dohon bhocchi konin dohonam kida giye.
\ip Bhethiroos Galila peente Beetesaydar dehea kaaran qazaate yisa ooninam wottsea eedine. Kisa kana Indirias Yesusbete kiam ki dhettsisade. Yesus tabhi lamaana kisa paanan yivaynaam yinin kamenka, igina iinte Bhethiroos kidi kalaa dahayse leve makkamna Yesussa kattsi nasho maatayse ki dahade. “Waani wul haam ke garaakaar inta haam garattine” hamayse yinin odimonsa budonte makkam goyt “Inta kiam dhesattine” hamayse Yesusam ki marimade. Ko dahaannaar Yesus dembhira kinin dhaabhonsa budonte Bhethiroosam yidar maasayse kisa tarjabee entsabe ki hayade. Yerusaalemir woysadhon misken ooninsa entsa gebha ki maatade.
\ip Bhethiroos warqatinam kinin thaapoono 52-56 levensa iintene hamayse koda bhocchadhe. Warqatam thaapadhon wodanka Bhethiroos thoothi leve Imbaa Yesusna waadadhayse ki gecchade. Imbaa Yesus Bhethiroos sadante gon hama gishiman gishea maatidine. Kidar woylamin qajayna waanina gon hama gishiman gishea kinin dohonam Bhethiroos kida giye. Ogonante waana waana taysate shedadhente gaalayna eenana kinin thaapenka, keam galshen bhocchin wulam Imbaa Yesusdar kenin dhaboadettsi kida bhocchise. Pir gon hamma maatayse waani Barjodar woylamin qajaana eenaam kenin gishoadettsi kida giye.
\ip Kaa mathaapaam raq tobbhaadar kashana dandima ko dandime:
\io1 1. Nagaymakkono (1:1-2)
\io1 2. Gaalen iinte wosa dohon qaabe haydhenam yedinta (1:3–2:10)
\io1 3. Gaalen iinte Barjosa bhocchinam haynta (2:11–4:6)
\io1 4. Gaalen iinte Barjona waadadhinta (4:7-11)
\io1 5. Gaalen iinte tarjinta (4:12-19)
\io1 6. Gaalen iinte wonin dhahayno wosa wotino (5:1-11)
\io1 7. Macchin nagaymakkono (5:12-14)
\ip Barjodar woylamin qajaana wonin dohonna gaalena wodi eldhidine. Harrna hambhidianna, Kiristoos wona hamayse gaalayse kisa paanan yivintaka wonin gaaloadettsi kamsi kidi maatidine (2:21). Gaalen wodar nivenka Barjo dhesa ki dhese; wona payya ki qaabade. Gaalensa iinte yer payya haya ko woam zaske. Wonin gaalonsa budonte Barjo gonin eena woam kida haye; wocchinsa ki wocchinse. Harrna hambhidianna, kisa gobshinam wo kashime kidi woam eelidine (5:10).
\ip Gaalena eelime wodar konin yeskenka lay dehen qaabe hayana Barjoka wonin adhadhonam woda dhese (1:3). Woylam wonin hayayno Barjobee kisa sunin imintonbekane (1:13bee 21be; 3:5). Barjo Kiristoosam dembhira kinin dhaasaadettsi woamaar dembhira dhaasa ki dhaase; rooro wul lay dehen kaymon raqinam cecinte wona kida ime (1:4). Wonin qaabe hayonam kidar woylam qajayse wonin yedenka, wosa gasante dohoono eeno haapayse targadhaate wosa qaabe haydinsa koda oyse (3:15). Ogodettsi wonin tiyayno gaaleno Kiristoossa wonin tarjoadettsi baali koda hapse. Ogona Barjona wosa daano elqimayse wona imbhon waadimankane. Barjona ee hamaate kina wosa dohon nashimmakkonam woda dhee.
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Yesus Kiristoos yisa tarjamonnante kinin yittsaa i Bhethirooskala, eedi pee eedi maataana Bhanthoosbee, Galatiabee, Qebhedoqiabee, Isiyabee, Bitaaniabe gidir wanthimayse dahaana Barjona kambhaanana nittsadhoono warqannone.
\v 2 Barjo Imbaa ena birayse qaabayse yeam ki kamade; Manpas Gazanoar yeam ko gazisade. Ogoka Yesus Kiristoosna ee ye hame kisa zombhinka ye yiithadhade. Barjosa sunin imintonbee payyamonbe yena ko thoothe.
\s1 Lay Dahayno Qaabe Wonin Hayayno
\p 
\v 3 Imbaa wontea Yesus Kiristoossa Imbaa Barjo ki gobshadhe. Kidi kattsi eedina garea yinin dohonna, Yesus Kiristoosin dembhira dhaabhon goynka lay dehen qaabe haydhenna woam haali adhayse,
\v 4 cecinte kaymabee, gemmimabee, gecchima raqbena woam ki ashkade.
\v 5 Yediar macchin rooroaka haapadhen dhaqintanna Barjodar woylamin yenin qajen goynka Barjosa kantanka toldhite ye dahade.
\v 6 Woda likkana taaki waana waana taysayse shedaynaka yeam gaale zaskidi ko hannaar, ogono yeam kattsi koda wozise.
\v 7 Ogono yesa taysate shedadhidino Barjodar woylamin yesa qajidinsa gonamonam shedanane. Worqi kayayno ko dahaakaar nuunte dhabayse koda shedadhe. Worqira sagi maatoono Barjodar woylamin yesa qajidinsa gonamono Yesus Kiristoosin haapadhen wodanka gobshinbee shawkadhanbeam koda hapse.
\v 8 Yesus Kiristoosam ye haapaammaar kiam nasheeda nashe; taaki kiam haapimina ye hannaar kidar woylamin qajeeda qaje; apoka giyana damadhimin gobshadhon wozanka yeda wozadhe.
\v 9 Harrna hambhidianna, kidar woylamin qajayse yenin toolen yesa sadansa dhaqintanam yenin haapennane.
\p 
\v 10 Yena imbhen Barjosa sunin imintonsa kikala qansayse giyaana eena ko dhaqintan goynsa kattsi payya hayayse ke marmarade.
\v 11 Kesa iinte dohoono Kiristoossa Manpasinoar kidar yesken gaalenbee ogosa budonte kinin haapen gobshinbeam ena birayse giydine. Kediar kono wul hamaa wodakabee hamin dahaa goytikabe konin maatenam may dhesana ke marmarade.
\v 12 Ogo yerinsa kenin giyenka kenin waadadhayno yenane, yimetensa kenin waadadhiminam Barjo kena may haydine. Taar cecira nittsadhon Manpas Gazansa kantanka Barjosa dhacchintan upsinam yena giyaanakalanka yedi qansidine; igina yerram Barjosa gaananaar shedana anngardhite ke dahade.
\s1 Gazamoka Daynta Zaskayno
\p 
\v 13 Ogonante yesa woylaminka qaymayse waadadhana ashkimbhee; yeam zaskaadettsi dehee; Yesus Kiristoosin haapadhen wodanka yenin tiyen Barjosa sunin imintondar qothimima qaabe hayee.
\v 14 Barjona ee hamayna maatayse, ena birayse dhesima yenin dohon siyon anngarmanka yiveebhode.
\v 15 Ko dahaannaar yeam eelaa Barjo gaza kinin dohondettsi, yediar dayntan yennon wulka gaza maataana eena dehee.
\v 16 Harrna hambhidianna, “Inta gaza inin dohonna yediar gazana eena maatee”\x - \xo 1:16 \xt Lewi 11:44; 19:2; 20:7. \x* hamayse thaapadhidine.
\p 
\v 17 Eedisa woti shedima een wulna yisa meteka meteka kesa waadimandettsi pirdeam “Imbo” hamayse eelayna ye hanna, ko yesa chocchamon wodanka kurtumbheka dehee.
\v 18 Harrna hambhidianna, yedi ena yesa eykenakalanka yenin tiyon ko pootimon dayntara yenin shandhoono kayen birre way worqika konin dahaamonam yedi dheseeda dhese.
\v 19 Yenin shandhoono yer siyabee wobobe yindar qolmaa yaatidettsi maataa Yesus Kiristoossa gobshadhon zombhinkane.
\v 20 Kinin dhesimoono peen pijadhima birayse ko hattaka, taaki wodansa macchinte yena hamayse ki haapadhade.
\v 21 Kiristooska dembhira kiam dhaasaa, gobshin kina imaa Barjodar woylamin yeda qaje; ogonante yesa woylamin qajidinbee qaabe haydinbe Barjodarne.
\p 
\v 22 Maltamoka dayma imbanaasdettsi kinka kiam kiam yenin nashoadettsi goninna ee hamada yesa woylaminam yedi gazinsidine. Ogonante kinka kiam kiam yesa woylaminka payya hayayse nashee.
\v 23 Lansi yenin adhadhoono rooro wul lay dehen Barjo upsin goynka kaya kayma bheetakalankane; kayea bheetakalankatehe.
\q1 
\v 24 “Eedi wul shudhidettsine;
\q1 kesa gobshinoar shudhisa aamadettsine.
\q1 Shundhoar waqaqa ko waqaqe, aamanoar diina ko diine.
\q1 
\v 25 Barjosa upsino ko hanna, rooro wul lay daa ko dee”\x - \xo 1:25 \xt Isi 40:6-8. \x*
\m hamayse thaapadhondettsine. Barjosa dhacchintan upsinsa yena giidhoono ogonone.
\c 2
\s1 Sadanka Dahaa Seeniabee Gazan Zarsinbe
\p 
\v 1 Ta keeda siyan wulbee, taysimen wulbee, maltamonbee, woogintonbee, eedi wuupintan wulbeam yedara marayse,
\v 2-3 Imbaa wontea Yesusin payya dohonam lavayse yenin haaponna, dhaqana kanka yenin gebhoadettsi taaki adhadhaana naana raathi kenin anngardhendettsi siyamoysa qolmon Barjosa upsinam anngardhee.
\p 
\v 4 Eenoar konin bagaa, Barjoyn kamaa, gobshadhaa sadanka dahaa sentakal theedate,
\v 5 yedi pir sadanka dahaana sennadettsi maatayse Yesus Kiristooska Barjoam wozisen manpasinngayn marshan imayna gazana gudulla yenin maatoadettsi, manpaska gaza oonidettsi woysadhite ye dahade.
\v 6 Harrna hambhidianna, Mathaap Gazante
\q1 “Marrato! Kambhaabee gobshadhaabe maataa
\q1 ooninam wocchinsea seeniam Thiyoonir ida wode;
\q1 kidar woylamin qajea ooshimbhehe”\x - \xo 2:6 \xt Isi 28:16. \x*
\m hamayse thaapadhidine.
\p 
\v 7 Ta keeda kidar woylamin qajayna yena kidi gobshadhaane. Kidar woylamin qajiminana ko hanna,
\q1 “Seeninka oonin woysayna eena kenin bagaa seenia
\q1 senna wulra ooninna kattsi zaskea ki maatade”\x - \xo 2:7 \xt Maz 118:22. \x*
\m 
\v 8 pir,
\q1 “Eedina goa maatea seenibee
\q1 eediam dhabea seeni laytabene”\x - \xo 2:8 \xt Isi 8:14. \x*
\m hamayse thaapadhondettsine. Kisa upsinam tiyma kenin garonna kanka keda dhambe; kediar birayse ogona ashkadhaanane.
\p 
\v 9 Yediar thipara tarshen yisa shaakante yeam eelaa Barjosa gebhon waadimanam yenin giyoadettsi, yedi kambhaana muldhana, bitaasa gudulla, Barjo yina kinin hayaana gazana zarsinane.
\v 10 Yedi ena Barjosa muldhatehe; ta yedi Barjosa muldha ye maatade. Yedi ena seesonsa garintonam haapeetene; ta yedi seesonsa garintonam ye haapade.
\s1 Barjona Waadadhayna
\p 
\v 11 Isa nashonato, peen kodar chocchibee eedi peera nivaanabe yenin dohonna, yesa sadanbesana banqin kansen yesa waansa anngarmakalanka yenin pegimbhoadettsi yeam ida miske.
\v 12 Yer hamin hambhaakaar Barjoam dhesimina “Siya keda waadadhe” hamayse yeam ke wuupaakaar, payyan yesa waadimanam kenin shedenka Barjo shedana kinin nivea rooroaka Barjoam kenin gobshoadettsi, kesa shaarinte yesa dayntano payya ko dee.
\p 
\v 13 Imbaa wontea Yesusna hamayse hayamoysa dahaana eena wulna ee hamee; gebhi hayamo kisa dohonna bitaana ee hamee;
\v 14 peen wottsaynanaar ee hamee. Harrna hambhidianna, kedi siyan waadadhaynaam dhabshana, payyan waadadhaynaam gobshana bitaakalanka nittsadhaana eenane.
\p 
\v 15 Barjosa bhocchino payyanam waadadhaate yer dhesimina malgimma eenasa dhalqinam lay yenin hayoadettsine.
\v 16 Barjona waadadhayna maatayse baza qolma dehee; baza qolma yenin dahayno siyamonam aachayno ko dahabhoode.
\v 17 Eedi wulam gobshee; Barjodar woylamin qajayna imbanaanaam nashee; Barjoam kurtumbhee; bitaam gobshee.
\s1 Kiristoos Gaalensa Kamsino
\p 
\v 18 Yedi eedina waadadhaynato, bhocchiysa payyanabee leeminabe bish dayma, bhocchiysa siya maataana yeam wottsaynanaar kurtumbheka ee hamee.
\v 19 Harrna hambhidianna, yiam zaskaamon dhabinam tiyea eedi Barjoam bhocchada gaalenam ki darshanna, gobshi kida haape.
\v 20 Seeso ye waadadhaysaka yeam qandhenka ye darshidianna, har gobshine yesa dohoono? Ko dahaannaar payya yenin waadadhonna yedar yesken gaalenam ye darshanna, ogoka Barjo birante shawkadhaana yeda maate.
\p 
\v 21 Yeam eldhoono ogonane. Kiristoos kisa paanan yenin yivoadettsi kamsi yena maatana yena hamayse gaalenam ki tiyade.
\v 22 Kidi seeso waadadhadehe; yisa aponkaar dhalq siya giyadehe.\x - \xo 2:22 \xt Isi 53:9. \x*
\v 23 Kiam kenin iirenkaar maasayse keam iiradehe; gaalenam yinin tiyenkaar keam kurtunsana upsi wocchi giyadehe.\x - \xo 2:23 \xt Isi 53:7. \x* Ko dahaannaar tipamonka pirdea Barjona yiam saskate ki imade.
\v 24 Wodi seesonna diyayse tipamonna wonin doadettsi, kidi yinti yisa waanka wosa seesonam masqalindar ki baskade; kisa hajiminka ye paashade.\x - \xo 2:24 \xt Isi 53:5. \x*
\v 25 Harrna hambhidianna, yedi yaatidettsi thar thar hamayse yaayayna ye dahade;\x - \xo 2:25 \xt Isi 53:6. \x* keeda yesa sadanam gisheabee tooleabedar ye maatade.
\c 3
\s1 Geshoabee Geshonbesa
\p 
\v 1 Ogodettsi yedi maanato, yesa annginana ee hamee. Waani Barjosa upsinna ee hamimina ke dahaannaar, upsi kala hattear ye giyma yesa dayntanka Barjodar maatasane.
\v 2 Barjodar kenin maatayno yesa gazan dayntanbee eediam gobshayna yenin maatonbeam yinin haapenkane.
\v 3 Yesa dantano mete ashkadhintabee, worqi arsintabee, gooben apalanam qaadhintabeka eenna haapadhen gommakkonka ko dahabhoode.
\v 4 Ko dahaannaar yesa dantano woylaminte aachimayse dohoono iin bishino ko dee. Ogono lemmakkobee lay haminta manpasbeysa dohoono kayma gommakkone; kosa bazano Barjo birante kattsi dethane.
\v 5 Ena wodanka Barjodar qaabe hayaana gazana maana pir yisa annginana ee hamaate ogodettsi yiam ke gobshade.
\v 6 Yin pir Saara Abraamam imbo hamayse eelada kina ee ko hamade. Yediar kala hattear kurtumbhima payya ye haydianna kosa naanane.
\p 
\v 7 Ogodettsi yedi annginato, kantaysa qolmina kenin dohonna yesa maanabesana bhocchika dehee. Yesa miskenam konin maroamadettsi, yembesana sadansa sunin imintonam tiyayna kenin dohonna keam gobshee.
\s1 Payya Waadadhintaka Gaalenam Tiynta
\p 
\v 8 Ta keeda yedi wul kinka bhocchi kalaaka kinka dehee; kinka kinka kina qaabee; kinka kiam indanaasdettsi nashee; eedina burqadhaynabee leemi maataana eenabe dehee.
\v 9 Siyon oolonte siyaka, iirimen oolonte iirimeka maaseebhode; ogosa oolonte kena Barjoam eelee. Harrna hambhidianna, yenin eldhoono ogoam hayntaka Barjokala imintonam yenin tiyoadettsine.
\v 10 Mathaap Gazanin giyendettsi:
\q1 “Sadanam nasheabee
\q1 payyan rooronam shedana zageabe
\q2 atabhinka yer siya kinin giyoamadettsi,
\q2 aponoar kisa dhalq siya konin giyoamadettsi
\q1 mete yisaam ki gishe.
\q1 
\v 11 Siyon yerinkalanka pegadhayse
\q2 payyan yerinam ki haye;
\q1 payyamonam ki zage; kanka ki yive.
\q1 
\v 12 Harrna hambhidianna, Barjosa aapino
\q1 tipan waadadhaynadar koda shede;
\q2 kisa qaaminoar kesa miskenam qansana bulimine.
\q1 Barjosa wacimen wotino siyon waadadhaynadarne”
\m hamayse ko thaapadhade.
\p 
\v 13 Payya waadadhana ye wocchimbhidianna yedar siya yeskisea hayne?
\v 14 Tipamon waadimanna hamayse gaalenam ye tiydiannaar yedi gobshadhaanane. Eenin yeam kurtunsenka kurtumbheebhode; gaaleebhode.
\v 15 Imbaa Kiristoosam yesa Imba hayayse woylaminka gobshee. Qaabe yenin hayen goynsa yeam oysaynana malsin maasana rooro wul ashkimbhaana dehee.
\v 16 Ko dahaannaar malsin yenin maasayno lemmakkobee gobshibeka ko dee. Kiristooska yesa dohon payyan dayntanam iirayna eena siya yenin hayaadettsi kenin wuupayna yerradar kenin ooshimbhoadettsi payya meske yesa ko dee.
\p 
\v 17 Barjosa bhocchino yin ko hanna, siya hayayse gaale yenin tiyenna payya hayayse gaalenam ye tiydianna yena payyane.
\v 18 Kiristoos pir woam Barjodar bavana, kidi tipa dahayse tipa maataamma wona hamayse, wosa seesonna kalaa goyt ki diyade. Waanka ki diyade; manpasinka lay dehea ki maatade.
\v 19 Ogo manpasinka dahayse dhaxin ooninte dahaana sadanana yivayse kena Barjosa upsinam ki giyade.
\v 20 Kediar Nohe gonngalanam kinin ashken wodanka Barjo darshada kinin kaalenka kina ee hamaamma eenane. Ogo gonngalansa iinte ardayse noqora dhaqaana eenasa paydino lankay bishne.
\v 21 Ogono noqono taaki yeam dhacchen shiidhimbhensa kamsine. Ogono shiidhimbheno yesa bishinsa dakan marayno dayma, payya meske haapana Barjokal theedea miskene; yeam konin dhacchayno Yesus Kiristoossa dembhira dhaabhidinkane.
\v 22 Kidiar cecindar yivayse Barjosa mizaqinte ki dahade; Barjosa gaananabee, hayamoysa dahaanabee, kantaysa dahaanabe kina ee hamite ke dahade.
\c 4
\s1 Gazamoka Dayntano
\p 
\v 1 Kiristoos yisa waanka gaale haapaa kinin dohonna, yediar banqin koymonam dhaximbha eadettsi ogo bhocchinka wocchimbhayse dehee. Harrna hambhidianna, yisa waanka gaale haapaa ea seeson waadimanam garidine.
\v 2 Keeda kaara os peen kogayn dayntanka yinin dehenka, eedisa anngarmaka dayma Barjosa bhocchinam thoosada kida dee.
\v 3 Barjoam dhesimina eenayn bhocchayno ogonoar sharmucimakkobee, siya anngardhintabee, baribee, warsabee, kattsi wucayse kirbintabee, aaninka ashkadhaana barjonana ooshinsen waadiman waadadhaate goodimintabe igina wulam ena yenin hayoono wodano yena yeeka ko yeeke.
\v 4 Kedi igina yerrasa anngarman thoothamonka kembesana kinka kalaa yenin maataamonna keda targadhe; yeam keda iire.
\v 5 Ko dahaannaar sadanka dahaanabee diyaanabedar pirdana ashkimbhaasa birante yisa waadimansa malsinam keda maase.
\v 6 Diyaanaar shidhima Barjosa dhacchintan upsinam kena giidhoono ogonane; eedidettsi kesa waandar pirdadhaakaar yisa manpasinka Barjoyn dehendettsi ke deene.
\s1 Barjosa Imintonaam Payyamoka Wottsinta Zaskayno
\p 
\v 7 Keeda yer wulsa macchino theedidine. Ogonante Barjoam miskana yenin damoadettsi qaymaa meske yesa ko dee; yeam zaskendettsi dehee.
\v 8 Nashimmakko seeson thoothinam konin kicenna,\x - \xo 4:8 \xt Kamn 10:12. \x* yer wulsa birayse kinka kiam kiam kattsi nashee.
\v 9 Gundume qolma kinka kiam kiam chocchamo tiyee.
\p 
\v 10 Waana waana Barjosa sunin imintonaam payya hayayse wottsintaka yennon iira eedi wul yisa meteka meteka yina imbhon sunin imintonka kinka kinka kina waadadhee.
\v 11 Eedi hayyear giyea yi hanna, Barjosa upsinam ki giye; waadadhea yi hannaar, Barjo kina imen kantanka ki waadadhe. Ogona Barjo yer wulka Yesus Kiristooska kida gobshadhe. Kina gobshibee hayamobe rooro wul lay ko dee; amiin.
\s1 Gaalen Rooroaka Wocchimbha Zaskayno
\p 
\v 12 Isa nashonato, nuudettsi maaton taysate sheden gaalensa iinte yenin dehenka dhesadhaama yer yedar nivaadettsi hayayse targadheebhode.
\v 13 Kalon Kiristoossa gobshinin may haapadhen wodanka kattsi yenin wozadhoadettsi, ta Kiristoossa gaalenam kashimayna yenin maatenka wozadhee.
\v 14 Kiristoossa naabenna hamayse ye irdhidianna, gobshadhaa Barjosa Manpasin yedar ukunsenna wozadhee.
\p 
\v 15 Yennon iira hayyear eediam deesintakabee, dimmakkokabee, siya hayntakabee, eedisa dhalqir ardintabeka gaale ki tiyabhoode.
\v 16 Ko dahaannaar Kiristoosdar woylamin qajea kinin dohonna gaale kidar yeskanna, ogo Kiristoossa naabenka Barjoam ki gobshe, ki ooshimbhabhoode.
\v 17 Pirdino Barjo eendar konin yedayno wodano yeskidine; birayse wodar yeskidi ko hanna, Barjosa dhacchintan upsinna ee hamiminasa kesa macchino hamin ko doo?
\q1 
\v 18 Tipaa ea gaaleka dhaqea ki hanna,
\q1 Barjoam kurtumbhimaabee seeson eabe hamin ki hame?\x - \xo 4:18 \xt Kamn 11:31. \x*
\m 
\v 19 Ogonante Barjosa bhocchidettsi gaalenam haapayna eena payyanam waadadhaate gon hama pijaa Barjona yisa sadanam ke ime.
\c 5
\s1 Barjo Eenaam Wottsadhen Goyno
\p 
\v 1 Ta keeda inta kembesana kinka misken ooninsa donza maataa, Kiristoos gaalensaar tarjea, os birante haapadhen kisa gobshinam kashimea dahayse, yesa shaarinte dahaana misken ooninsa donzanaam yin giyayse ida kiile:
\v 2 Yena elqimayse imbhaana Barjosa qollaam gishee. Ogonoar eedi yeam kantisonna dayma, Barjosa qaabondettsi nashayse keam toolee. Koymona gibazintaka dayma waadadhana yesa dohon payyan anngarmanka ko dee.
\v 3 Yenin wottsayna qollana kamsi maatee; kantanka keam wottseebhode.
\v 4 Yin ye hayanna, gishiman gishaynasa Hayoa Gebhaa kinin niven wodanka gemmimon gobshinsa qoobhenam yeda tiye.
\p 
\v 5 Yin pir yedi barshinato, donzanana ee hamee. Yedi wul mete toskintanam apaladettsi qaadhayse kinka kina waadadhee. Harrna hambhidianna, Barjo poorimbhaynaam jibba ki jibbe; metenam yisa toskaynana sunin imintonam ima ki ime.\x - \xo 5:5 \xt Kam 3:34. \x*
\v 6 Ta keeda Barjo yinin giyon wodanka yeam dheg kinin hayoadettsi, kisa kantan aanin demente yesa metenam toskee.
\v 7 Kidi yena kinin bhocchenna yeam galshen wulam kidar dhabee.\x - \xo 5:7 \xt Maz 55:22. \x*
\p 
\v 8 Ogonante yeam zaskendettsi qaymayse dehee. Harrna hambhidianna, yeam jibbea Seethaan yinin manngenam zagayse zobodettsi yesa gasante gudhite kida yaaye.
\v 9 Peen kodar dahaana yesa imbanaana ogodettsi gaale kenin tiyenam dhesayse, Barjodar woylamin yenin qajenka wocchimbhayse Seethaanam jibbee.
\v 10 Likka wodana gaalenam yenin tiyonsa budonte, Yesus Kiristooska rooro wul lay dehen kisa gobshinna yeam eelaa sunin iminton wulsa Barjo kidi yinti yeam maasayse wocchinsa ki wocchinse; yeam woysa ki woyse.
\v 11 Rooro wul lay bitamonbee kantanbe kina ko dee; amiin.
\s1 Macchin Nagaymakkono
\p 
\v 12 Eedi gon hama imbanaasine hamayse inin bhocchea Sillaasbar ko warqatinam likkaka yena i thaapade. Inin thaapoonoar yeam kiilanabee ogono gon Barjosa sun iminto konin dohonam yena tarjanabene. Ogonante Barjosa sunin imintonka wocchimbhayse woyee.
\p 
\v 13 Yembesana kinka kambhoono Baabiloon gidir dohon misken onno “Nagaya” yena koda hame; isa naasa Marqoosaar “Nagaya” yena kida hame.
\v 14 Nashimmakkoka kinka kiam sunqaate “Nagaya” kina hamee. Kiristooska maataana ye wulna payyamo ko dee. 
